{"tid":1283324,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"除咗「我冇嘢講」「我要見律師 」「我有權唔解鎖」仲有一樣嘢要留意","createTime":"2019-07-03T18:45:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T17:11:41.000Z","uid":23094,"like":39,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f572af36c524839fbce49c4504becabedd9ec392","tid":1283324,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T18:45:12.000Z","msg":"就係政府越高調製造白色恐怖<br />\n代表我哋越威脅到佢哋<br />\n即係我哋嘅方向越嚟越啱<br />\n<br />\n一個，兩個，三個<br />\n但係佢哋都從來冇企出嚟講過一句呀<br />\n你以為你就咁死咗佢哋就會良心發現咩？<br />\n只有繼續同佢哋鬥落去先可以激死佢哋<br />\n我哋一定會長命過呢班狗官同廢老<br />\n<br />\n覺得攰就休息，自然會有人接力<br />\n唞夠就再歸隊，隨時都歡迎<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以咁多位<br />\n一定要留返條命<br />\n一齊見證同創造歷史<br />\n而家唔准你死呀</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"316a90bdfc9c3d03b0a056ff49fb3026762d3cb9","tid":1283324,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T18:51:52.000Z","msg":"醒未<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfcc57221ae0871ba5c650c4b160420afaa03909","tid":1283324,"uid":115323,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T18:54:56.000Z","msg":"禁錯負皮屌"},{"pid":"a4d1adccefa5ab24efe27d4b6c073dcd7fa82eba","tid":1283324,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T18:55:35.000Z","msg":"你而家咁樣走咗嘅話<br />\n邊有面目見嗰3位義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34cdc2e00781325af30a2e54c903d6a59569ccb1","tid":1283324,"uid":264369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T18:58:32.000Z","msg":"政府越高調製造白色恐怖<br />\n可以係代表佢小氣<br />\n好撚好撚小氣"},{"pid":"cd3236db1fea0ab3761463e9b39f913c2c85f5ec","tid":1283324,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34cdc2e00781325af30a2e54c903d6a59569ccb1","tid":1283324,"uid":264369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T18:58:32.000Z","msg":"政府越高調製造白色恐怖<br />\n可以係代表佢小氣<br />\n好撚好撚小氣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T19:02:34.000Z","msg":"人民唔應該害怕政府<br />\n政府應該要害怕人民<br />\n<br />\n佢小氣即係佢唔輸得<br />\n即係我哋仲有贏嘅機會<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"883be65ce75ad27554d9eda34163fc29f5174054","tid":1283324,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T19:10:06.000Z","msg":"瞓前一推<br />\n<br />\n咁多位瞓覺好嘅<br />\n發個真嘅好夢<br />\n瞓醒再繼續發夢<br />\n<br />\n夢呢樣嘢絕對唔係不切實際<br />\n因為你前後左右永遠都會有人"},{"pid":"fe5da4f33ffc6baf159be5ee3ab5365a9c9926c3","tid":1283324,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T19:15:38.000Z","msg":"唔好淨係正評啦<br />\n幫手推<br />\n<br />\n你輕輕一推 可能可以挽救無數義士"},{"pid":"da6fd168c3a50ca7f3ebd0e63ff6730788192ed3","tid":1283324,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T00:32:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02d21c9f7312b57544d0b2264262605df4df0466","tid":1283324,"uid":67786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T04:19:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f93eb1f27af9dea3792b9c28a9e2ea0aa7ff3a4e","tid":1283324,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T04:44:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一齊贏</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f5adc8c9856a73bc3248e86285456e461035657","tid":1283324,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T09:40:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d822a39ffd594bb4f677b1398448f5e09cf85beb","tid":1283324,"uid":180114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T09:42:25.000Z","msg":"全民健身計劃<br />\n<br />\n黎緊我地進行義教，識，唔識都可以歡迎咁多位巴絲加入<br />\n<br />\n提提大家 呢個谷唔講任何政治 <br />\n只係單純想出嚟約大家做下健身 <br />\n記住 我地健身目的係為左以後俾人追可以跑快啲，搬野可以搬重啲,有危險可以保護到自己！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\